{
  "texts": [
    "The shared resource leads to mutual interference between the two functionalities.",
    "To deal with this problem, the ISAC-BS employs AI techniques for intelligent interference mitigation, which can be trained offline and performs online prediction with very low complexity.Qi et al. [223] investigated interference mitigation in uplink ISAC networks, whose system model was similar to that in Figure 16.",
    "They formulated a multiobjective optimization problem to balance the two functionalities.",
    "Specifically, the weighted sum of sensing and communication rate was maximized by jointly optimizing the transmitted waveform and beamforming at the receivers.",
    "In addition, they trained a DNN in a USL manner to handle the complicated non-convex optimization problem."
  ]
}